node.text: Todd McFarlane gives you the sneak peek of our upcoming My Hero Academia waves coming to McFarlane Toys!

node.text:
Batman with Battle Damage is available NOW exclusively at Target! Link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
In the Dark Multiverse, Batman wields an evil Black Lantern power ring, which grants him the power to resurrect the dead. Now he leads an army of zombies across a twisted hellish landscape and wages war against the The Batman Who Laughs to save the DC Multiverse!⁠
⁠
#DCMultiverse #DarkKnightMetal #McFarlaneToys

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McFarlane Toys on August 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
From Justice League: The Amazo Virus, we have not one but TWO incredible Batman Hazmat Suit 7” figures coming your way soon!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
The Batman Hazmat Suit (Gold Label) with Light Up chest logo will be found exclusively at Target for $29.99 USD. While the Batman Hazmat Suit with the regular chest logo is $19.99 USD and will be available at select retailers. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Stay tuned!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#DCMultiverse #McFarlaneToys

node.text:
The Flash from Superman: The Animated Series is available for Pre-Order NOW at select retailers. Link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
The Flash has mastery over not just speed, but time itself and always does his best to prevent tragedy from happening to the people of Central City and Keystone City. This 7" figure includes an accessory, an art card and a base for posing.⁠
⁠
#DCMultiverse #McFarlaneToys

Our Superman Black Suit Variant action figure is available for Pre-Order NOW at select retailers. Link in bio ⬆️⁠

⁠
#DCMultiverse #McFarlaneToys
